Class LevelTwo

java.lang.Object
com.example.demo.levels.LevelParent
com.example.demo.levels.LevelTwo
public class LevelTwo extends LevelParent
LevelTwo represents the second level of the game. It introduces more enemies and a higher kill target to advance to the next level.
